~z~Some shit just slammed into the fan, bro. I'm not gonna be able to make it to the show.
E1FCT2A.translated: ~z~突然遇上个大麻烦，兄弟。我没法来看演出了。

E1FCT2A.original: ~z~I didn't have you pegged as a cultural dude, Terry. Yeah, I'll go to a show. Give me an hour or two.
E1FCT2A.translated: ~z~没想到你还是个文化人啊，Terry。好，我来看演出。等我两个小时。

E1FCT2A.original: ~z~Air hockey? Not quite what I was expecting but, sure, why not...I'll swing by and pick you up.
E1FCT2A.translated: ~z~桌上冰球？这让我有点意外，不过也行吧...我一会儿过来接你。

E1FCT2A.original: ~z~Hey, it's Terry. Do you wanna go shoot some pool?
~z~Sure thing, Johnny, call me when you've got some free time.
~z~Sorry, Terry, air hockey's pretty far down my priority list right now. Maybe some other time.
E1FCT2A.translated: ~z~不好意思，Terry。我现在不太想打冰球。改天再说吧。
